section.response.block 
	.container 
		.response-grid 
			.response-grid__title 
				h2.response__title.text-uppercase.mb-0.text-center.text-lg-left Fast response <span class="text-blue">time</span>
			.response-grid__img
				img.img-rounded.response__img(src="img/response-img.jpg" alt="")
			.response-grid__description
				.response__description Every minute counts with water damage. Within 24 hours, water penetrates deeper into building materials, mould spores germinate, and structural damage accelerates. Our Sydney-based technicians arrive within 60 minutes on average — extracting water and starting the drying process before the damage compounds. Faster response means lower costs and faster recovery for you.
			.response-grid__btn
				.response__btn.text-center.text-lg-left
					+btn('btn btn-primary btn-rounded btn-large', 'SEND HELP NOW')